{"tid":527814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★其實「魚翅撈飯」時代，d人係strong hold or沽貨？","createTime":"2018-01-13T05:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T07:26:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1136fd68762e15e4c7d30045433a61af54c1d9ae","tid":527814,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:37:18.000Z","msg":"如果strong hold，根本冇賺過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n沽貨，唔通沽完，next day又買返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【港股大時代】詹培忠見證70年代　股民午、晚餐均「魚翅撈飯」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/133543_940ff8debb96b2d4eaac34637874e423.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F133543_940ff8debb96b2d4eaac34637874e423.jpg&h=1c48312b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在股票江湖打滾了近半個世紀的詹培忠，自23歲便開始接觸股票，在股票市場累積不少財富，見證過香港股票市場的盛衰。詹憶述，70年代的香港正值發展上升期，股市樓市大盛，令不少投資人士的戶口倍漲、消費力大增，市面上更流行着一種「食得招積」的魚翅撈飯；紅燒魚翅再配上白飯，基本上是每圍「常餐」，是投資者用來展示自己財力的表現，一碗平凡的白飯，要昂貴地以魚翅撈起來吃。詹稱，當時市價一碗魚翅撈飯由8元至30元不等，佔當時人均月入的四分之一，但大戶卻是天天吃，鄰近中環貿易場的茶樓食肆經常座無虛席。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">午飯、晚飯都食翅</span><br />\n<br />\n當時作為「少年股神」的詹培忠少不免也是天天魚翅撈飯的大戶之一。他回憶道，當時全香港酒樓都是賣翅，就連午飯、晚飯股民都要食翅，而且每日收市後，他經常有不同活動及應酬「收市後好多時會同埋一班行家去喜萬年酒樓食吓魚翅撈飯、打吓麻雀；有時甚至會去交換情報（即去夜總會）或者去遊艇派對玩。」他表示，現在自己仍不時有吃魚翅撈飯，「會久唔久去當年自己開創的佳寧娜酒樓食吓、回味吓」，但他不願透露現時魚翅撈飯的價錢，「唔講太多啦，費事人地覺得我晒命！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/149127/-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%A4%A7%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-%E8%A9%B9%E5%9F%B9%E5%BF%A0%E8%A6%8B%E8%AD%8970%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3-%E8%82%A1%E6%B0%91%E5%8D%88-%E6%99%9A%E9%A4%90%E5%9D%87-%E9%AD%9A%E7%BF%85%E6%92%88%E9%A3%AF-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F149127%2F-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3-%25E8%25A9%25B9%25E5%259F%25B9%25E5%25BF%25A0%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25AD%258970%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BB%25A3-%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258D%2588-%25E6%2599%259A%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%259D%2587-%25E9%25AD%259A%25E7%25BF%2585%25E6%2592%2588%25E9%25A3%25AF-&d=LP8yUVPm7W3rfFmF2OgoJv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=ae275d75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/149127/-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%A4%A7%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-%E8%A9%B9%E5%9F%B9%E5%BF%A0%E8%A6%8B%E8%AD%8970%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3-%E8%82%A1%E6%B0%91%E5%8D%88-%E6%99%9A%E9%A4%90%E5%9D%87-%E9%AD%9A%E7%BF%85%E6%92%88%E9%A3%AF-</a>"},{"pid":"abd71b633148e970f16a2d417e8385bb714bd07f","tid":527814,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93881884a777a3dbbfdb73693a8a27cf305ecda","tid":527814,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"個陣有錢真係晚晚叫雞屌到賓周軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0732eee1a83dda693ae3a9466f30ff3e5618bd4","tid":527814,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abd71b633148e970f16a2d417e8385bb714bd07f","tid":527814,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"老貓有冇食過"},{"pid":"42d33d287bc5d9dfec956c15db047564b4676411","tid":527814,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"同老貓相反就啱"},{"pid":"6ca7f7a74833c4e467a37bb8e30ccc35e77050c8","tid":527814,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c93881884a777a3dbbfdb73693a8a27cf305ecda","tid":527814,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"個陣有錢真係晚晚叫雞屌到賓周軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTi